I".<p><strong>Huge fiend (demon), chaotic evil</strong></p>

<p><strong>Armor Class</strong> 18 (natural armor)</p>

<p><strong>Hit Points</strong> 350 (28d12+168)</p>

<p><strong>Speed</strong> 30 ft.</p>

